PrecisEnactment of an ORDER PROHIBITING ENTRY ON CERTAIN LANDS IN THE YUKON TERRITORY (2001, NO. 01, FISHING BRANCH ECOLOGICAL RESERVE, Y.T. ) - which prohibits entry into certain areas of the Yukon for the purposes of prospecting or staking mineral claims, in order to protect an area known as the Fishing Branch Ecological Reserve.
